text: WDSV (91.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Greenville, Mississippi. The station is owned by Delta Foundation, Inc., and airs a community radio format. The station was assigned the WDSV call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on December 22, 2008. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for WDSV * DSV Category:Radio stations established in 2011 Category:2011 establishments in Mississippi Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Washington County, Mississippi
